{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a63417cc3fb48d65c6f", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 1, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 120, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba2"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "615d92eade3d91842a5cf7d4", "title": "JEE Main 2013 (23 Apr Online)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "A light ray falls on a square glass slab as shown in the diagram. The index of refraction of the glass, if total internal reflection is to occur at the vertical face, is equal to :\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/jb_8Ot4xcl5F-TsVxKL9an4_z6YQb_b1coR0JZCtNHU.original.fullsize.png\"><br>", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "18gav", "text": "\n$\\frac{(\\sqrt{2}+1)}{2}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "Q5T3y", "text": "\n$\\sqrt{\\frac{5}{2}}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "eWZ4v", "text": "\n$\\frac{3}{2}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "jSrcV", "text": "\n$\\sqrt{\\frac{3}{2}}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "At point A by Snell's law\n$$\n\\mu=\\frac{\\sin 45^{\\circ}}{\\sin r} \\Rightarrow \\sin r=\\frac{1}{\\mu \\sqrt{2}}\n$$\nAt point $\\mathrm{B}$, for total internal reflection,\n$$\n\\sin i_1=\\frac{1}{\\mu}\n$$\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/HBwMkP2Pl3VqPe6tcjzMNs9G7xWh36yvS99VdZcq0Is.original.fullsize.png\"><br>\nFrom figure, $i_1=90^{\\circ}-r$\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n& \\therefore\\left(\\sin 90^{\\circ}-r\\right)=\\frac{1}{\\mu} \\\\\n& \\Rightarrow \\cos r=\\frac{1}{\\mu}\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\nNow $\\cos r=\\sqrt{1-\\sin ^2 r}=\\sqrt{1-\\frac{1}{2 \\mu^2}}$\n$$\n=\\sqrt{\\frac{2 \\mu^2-1}{2 \\mu^2}}\n$$\nFrom eqs (ii) and (iii)\n$$\n\\frac{1}{\\mu}=\\sqrt{\\frac{2 \\mu^2-1}{2 \\mu^2}}\n$$\nSquaring both sides and then solving, we get\n$$\n\\mu=\\sqrt{\\frac{3}{2}}\n$$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ37458954", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["61964c922db938c3ec5c87e8", "6160243a86b518ff2afd9379", "6160243ae896b71d7f0f03d9", "61bb820fc1f688a120dfda9f", "61964c9102fe1de035852896", "61e7bd71a2dd607688d6c01b", "61c08989e3eba41a9e71354b", "61602437a04b762ba7dfcb47", "61602438690b07c861db4cc9", "6160243b7384a30f11cacc9e", "629109ef0299d67104ca49d5", "629f3a9295d059d5cc4d982e", "629621243e04d5d8ca7b92bd", "629f390e4eb9140dc965900d", "64eb06dd3118f713ecfef1b0", "66d5853ba75f05ee8564f575", "67921d651d5b5072da5e9aae", "67fdff46378e1624ea7b6984", "680920293a10446a207fdecb"], "cpyqbExams": ["615f0e999476412f48314daf", "616059af0283de43c87e3e23"]}}